      • providesRepositoryManagement

        public abstract boolean providesRepositoryManagement
        Determines if this connector provides the possibility for a user to create, edit or removal of repositories.

        Typically the expected value for a connector is to return true.

        Returns:
        true if this connector provides the possibility to create, edit or removal of repositories. Otherwise false.
